vue/html-quotes.good: <!-- good --> <template> <img src="./logo.png" /> </template>
vue/html-quotes.bad: <!-- bad --> <template> <div> <img src='./logo.png'> <img src=./logo.png> </div> </template>

vue/jsx-uses-vars.good: <!-- good --> <template> <div> yemb </div> </template> <script> export default { name: 'yemb', data() { return { a: 'a' } } } </script>
vue/jsx-uses-vars.bad: <!-- bad --> <script> import HelloWorld from './HelloWorld' export default { components: { HelloWorld }, render () { return ( <HelloWorld msg="world"/> ) } } </script>

vue/no-async-in-computed-properties.good: <!-- good --> <script> export default { computed: { foo() { let bar = 0 try { bar /= this.a } catch (e) { return 0 } return 1 } } } </script>
vue/no-async-in-computed-properties.bad: <!-- bad computed 内禁止包含异步方法 --> <script> export default { computed: { pro () { return Promise.all([new Promise((resolve, reject) => {})]) }, foo1: async function () { return await someFunc() }, bar () { return fetch(url).then(response => {}) }, tim () { setTimeout(() => { }, 0) }, inter () { setInterval(() => { }, 0) }, anim () { requestAnimationFrame(() => {}) } } } </script>

vue/no-duplicate-attributes.good: <!-- good --> <template> <div> <MyComponent :foo="abc" /> <MyComponent foo="abc" /> <MyComponent class="abc" :class="def" /> </div> </template>
vue/no-duplicate-attributes.bad: <!-- bad --> <template> <div> <MyComponent :foo="abc" foo="def" /> <MyComponent foo="abc" :foo="def" /> <MyComponent foo="abc" foo="def" /> <MyComponent :foo="abc" :foo="def" /> <MyComponent class="abc" class="def" /> </div> </template>

vue/no-multi-spaces.good: <!-- good --> <template> <div> <div class="foo" :style="bar" /> <i :class="{ 'fa-angle-up': isExpanded, 'fa-angle-down': !isExpanded }" /> </div> </template>
vue/no-multi-spaces.bad: <!-- bad --> <template> <div> <div class="foo" :style = "bar" /> <i :class="{ 'fa-angle-up' : isExpanded, 'fa-angle-down' : !isExpanded, }" /> </div> </template>

vue/no-parsing-error.good: <!-- good 正确的语法 --> <template> <div>{{ message }}</div> </template>
vue/no-parsing-error.bad: <!-- bad 错误的语法 --> <template> <div>{{message.}}</div> </template>

vue/no-reserved-keys.bad: <!-- bad 禁止覆盖保留字 --> <script> export default { props: { $el: String }, computed: { $on: { get () {} } }, data: { _foo: null }, methods: { $nextTick () {} } } </script>

vue/no-textarea-mustache.good: <!-- good --> <template> <textarea v-model="message" /> </template>
vue/no-textarea-mustache.bad: <!-- bad --> <template> <textarea>{{ message }}</textarea> </template>

vue/no-use-v-if-with-v-for.good: <!-- good --> <template> <div> <ul v-if="shown"> <TodoItem v-for="todo in todos" :key="todo.id" :todo="todo" :yemb="yemb" :cws="cws" :sdafd="asdf" /> </ul> </div> </template>
vue/no-use-v-if-with-v-for.bad: <!-- bad --> <template> <div> <TodoItem v-if="complete" v-for="todo in todos" :key="todo.id" :todo="todo" /> <TodoItem v-for="todo in todos" v-if="todo.shown" :key="todo.id" :todo="todo" /> </div> </template>

vue/order-in-components.good: <!-- good --> <script> export default { name: 'app', props: { propA: Number }, data() { return { msg: 'Welcome to Your Vue.js App' } } } </script>
vue/order-in-components.bad: <!-- bad --> <script> export default { name: 'app', data () { return { msg: 'Welcome to Your Vue.js App' } }, props: { propA: Number } } </script>

vue/require-component-is.good: <!-- good --> <template> <div> <div :is="type" /> <div v-bind:is="type" /> </div> </template>
vue/require-component-is.bad: <!-- bad --> <template> <component is="type"/> </template>

vue/require-render-return.good: <!-- good --> <script> export default { render(h) { return h('div', 'hello') } } </script>
vue/require-render-return.bad: <!-- bad --> <script> export default { render(h) { if (foo) { return h('div', 'hello') } } } </script>

vue/return-in-computed-property.good: <!-- good --> <script> export default { computed: { foo() { if (this.bar) { return this.baz } return this.baf }, bar() { return false } } } </script>
vue/return-in-computed-property.bad: <!-- bad --> <script> export default { computed: { baz() { if (this.baf) { return this.baf } }, baf() {} } } </script>

vue/valid-template-root.good: <!-- good --> <template> <div> <div>a</div> <p>b</p> </div> </template>
vue/valid-template-root.bad: <!-- bad --> <template> <div>hello</div> <div>hello</div> </template> <template>Lorem ipsum</template> <template></template> <template> <div v-for="item in items"/> </template>

vue/valid-v-bind.good: <!-- good 语法正确的 v-bind --> <template> <div> <div v-bind="foo"></div> <div v-bind:aaa="foo"></div> <div :aaa="foo"></div> <div :aaa.prop="foo"></div> </div> </template>
vue/valid-v-bind.bad: <!-- bad 语法错误的 v-bind --> <template> <div> <div v-bind></div> <div :aaa></div> <div v-bind:aaa.bbb="foo"></div> </div> </template>

vue/valid-v-cloak.good: <!-- good --> <template> <!-- ✓ GOOD --> <div v-cloak /> </template>
vue/valid-v-cloak.bad: <!-- bad --> <template> <div v-cloak:aaa/> </template> <template> <div v-cloak.bbb/> </template> <template> <div v-cloak="ccc"/> </template>

vue/valid-v-else.good: <!-- good --> <template> <div> <div v-if="foo" /> <div v-else /> </div> </template>
vue/valid-v-else.bad: <!-- bad --> <template> <div v-if="foo"/> <div v-else="foo"/> <!-- bad <div v-else:aaa/> <div v-else.bbb/> --> </template>

vue/valid-v-else-if.good: <!-- good --> <template> <div> <div v-if="foo" /> <div v-else-if="bar" /> </div> </template>
vue/valid-v-else-if.bad: <!-- bad --> <template> <div v-if="foo"/> <div v-else-if/> <!-- bad <div v-else-if:aaa="foo"/> <div v-else-if.bbb="foo"/> --> </template>

vue/valid-v-for.good: <!-- good --> <template> <div> <div v-for="todo in todos" :key="todo.id" /> <MyComponent v-for="todo in todos" :key="todo.id" /> <div v-for="todo in todos" :is="MyComponent" :key="todo.id" /> </div> </template>
vue/valid-v-for.bad: <!-- bad require-v-for-key 也属于一部分 --> <template> <div> <div v-for/> <div v-for:aaa="todo in todos"/> <div v-for.bbb="todo in todos"/> <div v-for="todo in todos" is="MyComponent" /> <MyComponent v-for="todo in todos"/> <MyComponent v-for="todo in todos" :key="foo" /> </div> </template>

vue/valid-v-html.good: <!-- good --> <template> <div v-html="foo" /> </template>
vue/valid-v-html.bad: <!-- bad --> <template> <div> <div v-html /> <div v-html:aaa="foo"/> <div v-html.bbb="foo"/> </div> </template>

vue/valid-v-if.good: <!-- good --> <template> <div> <div v-if="foo" /> <div v-else-if="bar" /> <div v-else /> </div> </template>
vue/valid-v-if.bad: <!-- bad --> <template> <div> <div v-if/> <div v-if:aaa="foo"/> <div v-if.bbb="foo"/> <div v-if="foo" v-else /> <div v-if="foo" v-else-if="bar" /> </div> </template>

vue/valid-v-model.good: <!-- good --> <template> <div> <input v-model="foo" /> <input v-model.lazy="foo" /> <textarea v-model="foo" /> <MyComponent v-model="foo" /> <div v-for="todo in todos" :key="todo.key"> <input v-model="todo.name" /> </div> </div> </template>
vue/valid-v-model.bad: <!-- bad --> <template> <div> <input v-model> <input v-model:aaa="foo"> <input v-model.bbb="foo"> <input v-model="foo + bar"> <div v-model="foo"/> <div v-for="todo in todos"> <input v-model="todo"> </div> </div> </template>

vue/valid-v-on.good: <!-- good --> <template> <div> <div v-on="foo" /> <div v-on:click="foo" /> <div @click="foo" /> <div @click.left="foo" /> <div @click.prevent /> <div @click.stop /> </div> </template>
vue/valid-v-on.bad: <!-- bad --> <template> <div> <div v-on/> <div v-on:click/> <div v-on:click.aaa="foo"/> <div @click/> </div> </template>

vue/valid-v-once.good: <!-- good --> <template> <div v-once /> </template>
vue/valid-v-once.bad: <!-- bad --> <template> <div> <div v-once:aaa/> <div v-once.bbb/> <div v-once="ccc"/> </div> </template>

vue/valid-v-pre.good: <!-- good --> <template> <div v-pre /> </template>
vue/valid-v-pre.bad: <!-- bad --> <template> <div> <div v-pre:aaa/> <div v-pre.bbb/> <div v-pre="ccc"/> </div> </template>

vue/valid-v-show.good: <!-- good --> <template> <div v-show="foo" /> </template>
vue/valid-v-show.bad: <!-- bad --> <template> <div> <div v-show/> <div v-show:aaa="foo"/> <div v-show.bbb="foo"/> </div> </template>

vue/valid-v-text.good: <!-- good --> <template> <div v-text="foo" /> </template>
vue/valid-v-text.bad: <!-- bad --> <template> <div> <div v-text:aaa="foo"/> <div v-text.bbb="foo"/> </div> </template>
